<DATE_TIME> 1998-10-01 16:53 </DATE_TIME>
<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Istanbul Stock Exchange Index Down </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ANKARA, October 1 (Xinhua) -- Turkey's Istanbul Stock
Exchange National-100 Index closed at 2,085.50 on Thursday, down
180.44 points, or 94 percent, from Wednesday's finish.
</P>
<P>
The trading was active with the turnover reaching over 42
trillion Turkish Liras (over 153 million U.S. dollars).
</P>
<P>
The financial index went down 222.10 points, or 9.71
percent, to close at 2,465.59 points, the industrial index fell
143.10 points, or 7.34 percent, to close at 1,814.82 points,
and the service index dropped 169.39 points, or 5.45 percent,
to close at 2,920.60 points. 
</P>
</TEXT>
