The Kurdish deputies hold a discussion Wednesday in the Italian
parliament building on the future of the Kurds in Turkey.
</P>
<P>
Turkish Foreign Ministry issued a statement Tuesday accusing
Italy of supporting the separatist activities by the PKK which
has been fighting for autonomy in southeastern Turkey since 1984.
