<TEXT>
<P>
WASHINGTON, October 1 (Xinhua) -- The Inter-American
Development Bank (IDB) Thursday announced the approval of a 19.4
million U.S. dollar concessional loan to Haiti to support the
first phase of the government's basic education project.
</P>
<P>
