In the women's semi-finals, third seed Cassie Jackman of
Britain beat the top seed Sarah Fitz-Gerald of Australia 7-9,
5-9, 9-7, 9-4, 9-1 while second seeded Michelle Martin of
Australia edged 8th seed Leilani Joyce of New Zealand 0-9, 9-3,
9-5, 9-1. 
